frontmatter.title: The Backwoods
frontmatter.productDescription: A Sun Holiday Pool is constructed with three quarter inch pressure treated wood sidewalls.The wood is impregnated with preservatives to resist decay and termites - even when in direct contact with the ground. Lifetime Warranty to the original consumer purchaser. All in ground pools include gravel back fill and a water drainage tile system.
frontmatter.subtitle: Hand crafted to Perfection
